+// Edge-aware 2x2 downsample for the push-pull pyramid (replaces hardware GenerateMips).
+// For each output pixel, reads the 2x2 region of the previous level, picks the
+// most-confident input's luminance as a "region reference", then averages all 4
+// weighted by (confidence * exp(-|luma_i - ref| * k)). Inputs across an object
+// boundary get vanishing weight, so the dominant region's colour stays dominant
+// at every coarser level -- no Gaussian-style yellow-green-from-the-boundary
+// averages that produce the blob fills in interiors.
